Class StudySpaceParametersProvider

  • java.lang.Object

  • public class StudySpaceParametersProvider
extends java.lang.Object
    StudySpaceParametersProvider class is used to talk to WiseStudySpaceWizard and get all the parameters related to study paces in the system.
